import { CardContainer, Header, Title, CampaingId, Info, Footer, FirstFunilStep, FunilStep, LastFunilStep, TitleStep, ContentStep, TextContent } from './styles' interface Props { id: number name: string income: number totalClicks: number totalProductPage: number totalCheckoutPage: number totalPaidClicks: number } const SummaryCard = ({ id, name, income, totalClicks, totalProductPage, totalCheckoutPage, totalPaidClicks }: Props) => { return (
{name} id campanha: {id}
Página de Noticias {totalClicks} Total de Pessoas que acessaram a página: Página de Compra {totalProductPage} Checkout {totalCheckoutPage} Pagos {totalPaidClicks}
Taxa de conversão {totalPaidClicks/totalClicks*100}%
Faturamento R${income}
 ) } export default SummaryCard
